minors. Ryan, who has been trying to come back from major elbow 
surgery since 1997, accepted an assignment to Triple-A Scranton in 
May. Phillies general manager Ed Wade said he wanted to give Ryan 
the option to sign with another team before the end of the season. 
  	   	
